        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Lesson #1",
            "id": 131820,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Let's explore using <code>continue</code>, <code>break</code>, and <code>else</code> to control the loop flow, skip iterations, exit early, or run code after the loop.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2 - Copy",
            "id": 131844,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>continue</code> is used to skip the current block and move to the next iteration.</p><p>Ensure to not print the number <code>2</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&gt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>==</code>, followed by <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 131821,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Use <code>continue</code> to skip over specific elements, like <code>\"chips\"</code> in a loop, and move to the next iteration.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shopping_list = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;apples&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;bananas&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;bread&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;milk&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;chips&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;eggs&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" item \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" shopping_list:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" item == \" /><text value=\"&quot;chips&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Don't forget to buy: \" /><text value=\"{item}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"126\" endIndex=\"134\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: apples\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: bananas\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: bread\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: milk\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't forget to buy: eggs\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 131845,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>The <code>break</code> statement exits the loop entirely. If it is invoked, it doesn't execute the rest of the iterations.</p><p>Let's add a <code>break</code> statement to the program to stop the loop when <code>i</code> becomes <code>3</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>==</code>, followed by <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 131823,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We can use the <code>break</code> keyword to break out of a <code>while</code> loop if a certain condition is met, like a matching password.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"password = \" /><text value=\"&quot;open_sesame&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" input(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Enter the password: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") == password:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Access granted!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Incorrect password. Try again.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"119\" endIndex=\"124\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Incorrect password. Try again.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Incorrect password. Try again.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Access granted!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to type <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 131825,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Finally, the <code>else</code> statement in loops is executed when the loop has finished. Remember, <code>else</code> in a loop differs from <code>else</code> in an <code>if</code> statement.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"'Loop has ended'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"37\" /><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loop has ended\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>else</code>, followed by <code>:</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 131826,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>The <code>else</code> block will only be executed if the loop is not terminated early by a <code>break</code> statement.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"11\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i == \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loop has ended.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"62\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>break</code>, followed by <code>else:</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 131868,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code the missing keyword to print a final statement after the loop went through all items.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shows = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;The Office&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Dexter&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Friends&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" show \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" shows:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(show)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Those are my favorite shows!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"78\" endIndex=\"82\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"break\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"continue\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"The Office\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Dexter\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Friends\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Those are my favorite shows!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>else</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 131869,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Which keyword skips the rest of the current loop's block?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>continue</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>break</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 131870,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ensure that we are not processing completed tasks.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"tasks = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;completed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"index = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" index &lt; len(tasks):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" tasks[index] == \" /><text value=\"&quot;completed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Skipping task \" /><text value=\"{index + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    index += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Processing task \" /><text value=\"{index + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  index += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"185\" endIndex=\"193\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"break\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"else\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Processing task 1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Skipping task 2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Processing task 3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Processing task 4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 131871,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Which keyword breaks out of a loop immediately?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>break</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>continue</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #6",
            "id": 131872,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Be sure to fix the bugs instead of continuing with the to-do list.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"tasks = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;email boss&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;attend meeting&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" task \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" tasks:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" task == \" /><text value=\"&quot;fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Urgent task found: fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Working on: \" /><text value=\"{task}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"81\" /><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"140\" endIndex=\"145\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"else\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"continue\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Working on: email boss\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Urgent task found: fix bug\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>task</code> followed by <code>==</code> and then <code>\"fix bug\"</code>, <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
